with this traitor!

00:20:50.875 --> 00:20:52.961 position:50% align:center
Eh? Please explain.

00:20:53.044 --> 00:20:55.547 position:50% align:center
Because, as per usual,
I'm very confused.

00:20:55.630 --> 00:20:57.549 position:50% align:center
[KINJI] I feel like it's
self-explanatory.

00:20:57.632 --> 00:20:59.384 position:50% align:center
She found out we're
teaming up with monsters

00:20:59.467 --> 00:21:00.635 position:50% align:center
and now she's our prisoner.

00:21:00.719 --> 00:21:04.014 position:50% align:center
Ah! Miss Shia, of all
the people in the world?

00:21:04.097 --> 00:21:05.181 position:50% align:center
That's gotta be
the worst hostage

00:21:05.265 --> 00:21:06.683 position:50% align:center
