00:21:06.766 --> 00:21:09.269 position:50% align:center
I'm reporting this as soon as
I get free, mark my words.

00:21:09.352 --> 00:21:10.395 position:50% align:center
And for what it's worth,

00:21:10.478 --> 00:21:12.522 position:50% align:center
