never forgive you!

00:21:12.605 --> 00:21:15.066 position:50% align:center
Aw, geez.
This is beyond bad news.

00:21:15.150 --> 00:21:16.776 position:50% align:center
What's gonna happen to us
if the company

00:21:16.860 --> 00:21:18.653 position:50% align:center
finds out what we're
doing down here?

00:21:18.737 --> 00:21:23.158 position:50% align:center
Not to worry, my reptilian
friend. Luckily, I have a plan.

00:21:23.241 --> 00:21:25.660 position:50% align:center
Did you bring the camera,
like I asked you?

00:21:25.744 --> 00:21:28.955 position:50% align:center
Wait. Um. What are you scheming?

00:21:31.041 --> 00:21:32.792 position:50% align:center
[KINJI, ANT QUEEN laughing]

00:21:32.876 --> 00:21:33.960 position:50% align:center
Man! How great is this?

00:21:34.044 --> 00:21:35.462 position:50% align:center
Indeed!

00:21:35.545 --> 00:21:37.088 position:50% align:center
So, unless you want the world
to see their favorite hero

00:21:37.172 --> 00:21:38.965 position:50% align:center
getting chummy
with her monster pals,

00:21:39.049 --> 00:21:41.760 position:50% align:center
keep your lips zipped
'bout everything you saw!

00:21:41.843 --> 00:21:43.511 position:50% align:center
[SHIA gasps]
You wouldn't dare!

00:21:43.595 --> 00:21:45.096 position:50% align:center
Please say it ain't so.

00:21:45.180 --> 00:21:46.765 position:50% align:center
The only reason you
had me bring the camera

00:21:46.848 --> 00:21:49.017 position:50% align:center
was so that you could
blackmail Miss Shia?

00:21:49.100 --> 00:21:50.727 position:50% align:center
You are just downright evil!

00:21:50.810 --> 00:21:53.355 position:50% align:center
And I conquer all evil
that crosses my path!

00:21:53.438 --> 00:21:54.647 position:50% align:center
[KINJI] Since you're
officially one of us,

00:21:54.731 --> 00:21:56.983 position:50% align:center
you really shouldn't
threaten your colleagues.

00:21:57.067 --> 00:21:59.402 position:50% align:center
Now be sure to put that
stellar work ethic of yours

00:21:59.486 --> 00:22:02.197 position:50% align:center
to good use for the Dungeon
Black Company, all right?

00:22:02.280 --> 00:22:05.116 position:50% align:center
What the heck is a
Dungeon Black Company?

00:22:05.200 --> 00:22:08.745 position:50% align:center
If it's anything like it sounds,
there's no doubt it's dreadful!

00:22:08.828 --> 00:22:13.833 position:50% align:center
[KINJI laughing]